@start_at = 1776960000
@end_at = 1777046399

### 获取注单（gamerecord，历史注单）
# 路径: {apiUrl}/ley/gamerecord，POST，application/x-www-form-urlencoded
# 必填/实际发送: account, api_key, method, page, pageSize, start_at, end_at
#   method: betTime=按投注时间（代码固定）；部分文档另有 updateTime
#   pageSize: 1～500，超过 500 时代码会钳到 500
# 与 XH 对齐：可选附带 username（与源码中非空 player_name 一致）；未列出的 api_code、currency、status 仍不传
POST {{host}}/ley/gamerecord HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

account={{account}}
&api_key={{api_key}}
&method={{method}}
&page={{page}}
&pageSize={{pageSize}}
&start_at={{start_at}}
&end_at={{end_at}}

